            %p.light Intuitive usage. You just enter you items, select or create a customer and hit tab and generate a PDF.
        .col.s12.m4
          .icon-block
            %h2.center.brown-text
              %i.material-icons settings
            %h5.center Full control
            %p.light No standard invoice templates, with just a bit knowledge of html/css you have full control.
        .col.s12.m4
          .icon-block
            %h2.center.brown-text
              %i.material-icons verified_user
            %h5.center No shit!
            %p.light With Zelos you use a open-source software. Nobody gets rich and we won't destroy the rainforest.


